# JONBEATZ.DEV — Core Rules

Standalone red command-center site (`jonbeatz.dev`). Self-contained Next.js + Three.js
project split out of the JonBeatz personal profile. Detailed rules live in `.cursor/rules/`.

## Source of truth order

1. `TRUTH.md`
2. `.cursor/docs/START-HERE.md`
3. `.cursor/docs/MASTER-COMMANDS.md`
4. `.cursor/docs/JONBEATZ-DEV-DEPLOY.md`
5. `.cursor/docs/HOSTINGER-REFERENCE.md`
6. `.cursor/docs/ReCall.md`

## Hard boundaries

- **Included:** OmniVoice (JARVIS, ritual-only — see `.cursor/rules/voice-policy.mdc`) +
  project MCPs (21st-dev, markdownify, browserbase, pencil, composio).
- **Stay personal** (`D:\Hermes\projects\JonBeatz`): Telegram, DeepSeek/LiteLLM, ComfyUI,
  Google, image-gen.
- **No gold `jon-beatz.com`** here — this repo ships only the red `jonbeatz.dev`.
- **Mem0 scope = `jonbeatz_dev`** only.

## Safety defaults

- Windows PowerShell. No bash heredocs. Never commit `.env*` or `.cursor/mcp.json`
  (gitignored — repo is public; commit only `*.example`).
- UTF-8: use `npm run version:sync` for badges; `npm run encoding:check` before doc commits.

## Skills (read before relevant work)

UI: NovaMira-Design → MSC-UI-Taste → Premium-UI → DesignMD. Code: Nova.
3D/WebGL: 3D-Modeling, 3D-Scroll, Three.js-Ops, WebGL-UI. Git: GitHub-Ops. Deploy: Hostinger-Ops.

## Session rituals

| Jon says | Action |
|----------|--------|
| Start Project / Start Session / Cold Start | `.cursor/prompts/Start-Project.md` + `npm run session:start` |
| End Project / End Session | `.cursor/prompts/End-Project.md` + `npm run session:stop` |
| update docs | `.cursor/prompts/Update-Docs.md` + `npm run docs:sync` |
| backup / backup full | `npm run backup:quick` / `backup:quick:full` (interactive for backup project) |
| branch cut | `.cursor/prompts/Branch-Cut.md` |
| release version | `.cursor/prompts/Release-Version.md` |

See `.cursor/rules/workflow.mdc` for the full trigger map.
